Title: Instinct
Plot: H.G. has created a new life for herself in Wisconsin, but calls in the agents when she comes up against an unidentified artifact. Meanwhile, Abigail joins the others on the floor of the Warehouse to track down the source of mysterious tremors that threaten to destroy the building.
GuestStars: Kelly Hu, Todd Stashwick, Tuc Watkins, Ricardo Chavira, Jaime Murray, Eric Murdoch, Imali Perera
